<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ ạ̹lhy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ ạ̹lhy fy qrbk ạ̉frḥ ṭwl ạlmdy̱
 yạạ̹lhy bʿwnk ạ̉qhr jysẖ ạlʿdy̱
 ạlqrạr- yạ ạ̹lhy yạ ḥbyby yạ mnthy̱ ạlḥb
 (wjhk ạlwḍạḥ lạ̉jly yạ msẖbʿ ạlqlb)2
 2- yạ ạ̹lhy fy ḥbk ymsḥ ly dmʿty
 yạ msyḥy bṣlbk qd gẖfrt dẖlty
 3- yạ ḥbyby yạ rạḥty ạ̉rtmy fy ḥḍnk
 fy ḥnạn fyh slạm ạ̉ʿṭyny mn ḥbk</lyrics>
<hymn_number>7019</hymn_number>
</song>